      "reviews": [
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Doesn\u2019t get the credit it deserves! Will only use this!",
          "reviewText": "Love love love this! Best foundation I have used! I have mature skin, oily Tzone/ combination skin. I swear I have tried everything. Est\u00e9e Lauder, Dior, Haus labs, elf, L\u2019Or\u00e9al, Maybelline, two faced, Fenty, Mac, Nix, unnamed brands. From expensive to not expensive and nothing really seemed to work. It would either pill on my face, oxidize, look oily, and after hours it looked like a mess. This is with toner, moisturizer, and a primer all put on. I thought I would just try this airbrush makeup since I never tried anything airbrush before and it\u2019s the holy grail of foundation! So easy to apply, stays on for hours, doesn\u2019t get oily, and actually covers your face. Plus you can build it up and it still looks flawless and lightweight. Other expensive brands you build up and you can tell you have a ton of makeup on. Not with this! I wish I would have tried this earlier! Would have saved me a crap load of money! I\u2019m just amazed at how long the wear of it is on my face. Even kept it on going to the gym and through a workout and I still looked great afterwards. Highly recommend!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on March 20, 2025",
          "customer": "Becky verfuerth",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AEP2LANTWUQJJJWT6T2LANPNG4QQ",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
            "color": "04 Light Medium",
            "size": "1.8 Fl Oz (70 ml)"
          },
          "helpfulVotes": "64 people found this helpful"
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Functionality",
          "reviewText": "Im 47 and love this foundation. It works well for mature skin. It also blends in nicely and is a great color match. This foundation creates a natural look which I love. I have tried tons of foundations throughout the years and this is the only one I buy!",
