        {
          "reviewTitle": "Great lightweight foundation with good coverage!",
          "reviewText": "This makeup was delivered just as promised and is exactly the shade and 2 I ordered. And by the way this make is wonderful for mature skin, gliding without caking and covers blemishes and age spots so well! It\u2019s the only foundation I have used for several years now!",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on March 27, 2026",
