        {
          "reviewTitle": "Found my shade",
          "reviewText": "I\u2019ve bought this five or six times and received compliments on my skin looking glowy or tanned. I had 3 different shades and never felt like it was exactly right. Finally tried a fourth shade because I loved the formula and feel of the makeup. Dead on match. I sometimes mix the shades one on top of the other depending on season. Fantastic makeup. Lasts a long time because you only need a couple of sprays for good coverage. It gives much better results than the more expensive ones. I have also purchased half a dozen other foundations this past year including giving in to the relentless ads for il makiage. I keep going back to Jerome Alexander.",
          "reviewDate": "Reviewed in the United States on March 13, 2026",
          "customer": "LC",
          "customerProfileUrl": "https://www.amazon.com/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AFWX4QQGNJMVLQYEXK57N7VIWV7A",
          "customerStarsRating": 5,
          "productSpecs": {
            "color": "01 Fair",
            "size": "1.8 Fl Oz (70 ml)"
          }
        },
        {
          "reviewTitle": "Great for mature skin. Goes on evenly and smoothly.",
