        {
          "reviewTitle": "Great option",
          "reviewText": "I used to use the designer brand E.L. and their prices kept increasing exponentially, I figured why not give this a try, and I\u2019m SO glad I did! For a fraction of the price this is a beautiful, creamy, buildable foundation that lasts a nice long time. Highly recommend!",
